Package com.i2group.apollo.model.security.transport

Contains classes for communicating security information with i2 Analyze services.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SecuritySchema
    A container for the SecurityDimensions and SecurityTagGroups that can be used for Items in i2 Analyze.
    SecurityTag
    A named container for SecurityAccessPermissions and SecurityGrantPermissions that can be used to provide security information for an Item.
    SecurityTagGroup
    A container for SecurityTags that also specifies whether (and how many of) the SecurityTags that it contains must be present on Items that use security tagging.
